                                         Appium
IOS and Android :

- Native Applications
- Hybrid Applications (combination of native and web) apks.
- Mobile Web
- Flutter based applications

https://appium.io/
Download Appium desktop application

preRequisites:-
1. Python
2. PvCharm
3. JDK 11
4. NodeJS latest version
5. Android Studio
6. Appium CLI Server
7. Appium Drivers
8. Appium Inspector
9. XCUI Test Driver
10. UI Automator 2
11. Appium Client

Installation Appium CLI Server :-
- npm install -g appium@next (g: global)

Installation Appium Drivers :-
appium driver install [installation key] (refer website)

Installation Appium Inspector :-
- separate app
- https://github.com/appium/appium-inspector/releases


